api_list.name: Get random Names
api_list.description:
This endpoint will return an array of X(count) random names. 
If you don't specify a count value it will default to 10.

[

api_list.name: Get random Dates
api_list.description:
This endpoint will return an array of X(count) random dates betweeen a start year and a end year. 
If you don't specify a count value it will default to 10.
If you don't specify a start year value it will default to 1900. 
If you don't specify a end year value it will default to 2023.

Response will look like:

[
  "1997-05-01T00:00:00",
  "1995-01-25T00:00:00",
  "2011-01-16T00:00:00",
  "1964-02-06T00:00:00",
  "2015-09-26T00:00:00",
  "1955-11-20T00:00:00",
  "1961-01-27T00:00:00",
  "1952-06-17T00:00:00",
  "1924-05-01T00:00:00",
  "2001-11-12T00:00:00"
]
